  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Send 2100 Children in Slums to Schools</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">DoPeace is formed to bring the little children of the slums of the world into classrooms. Since 2014, we have enrolled more than 10,000 children in the slums of Bangladesh. We have developed an infrastructure of five NGOs, 100 teachers and professionals, and 45 one-room schools in five slums. This project is to add 10 schools, bringing 2100 little children  into the classrooms. We operate the schools at the low cost of $1/child/month. Thus, the project cost is $25,200 for one year.</narrative>
  </description>
